# Fonts to install into the renderer image via `fnt` (apt for fonts), one name
# per line; blank lines and #-comments are ignored. Both these fonts are also
# subsetted and embedded into every SVG (see Dockerfile) so diagrams display in
# them in any viewer. Add more here for measurement as needed.
#
# Note: the DEFAULT diagram font is **Jost**, which is NOT in fnt's catalog (nor
# apt) — the Dockerfile fetches it directly from Google Fonts. Roboto stays
# available (kept here) and is also embedded; authors can opt into it with
# `skinparam defaultFontName Roboto`.
#
# `fnt` always fetches the latest font from the network at build time — it does
# not pin versions, so this renderer is intentionally NOT a reproducible,
# offline, digest-pinned build (unlike the digest-pinned base image). See README.md.
fonts-roboto-unhinted
